      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey my head has been hurting pretty bad for the last few hours and i cant really shake it. i take warfarin for my heart stuff so i have to be careful with meds but would it be okay if i just took some ibuprofen to help with the pain? it's a pretty standard headache so i figured it should be fine right?",
